Paper: hep-th/0210077

Date: 2002-10-08

Title: Ghost condensates in Yang-Mills theories in the Landau gauge

Authors: V.E.R. Lemes, M.S. Sarandy, and S.P. Sorella

Comments: 24 pages, references added, final version to appear in Ann. of Phys

Ghost condensates of dimension two are analysed in pure SU(N) Yang-Millstheories by combining the local composite operators technique with thealgebraic BRST renormalization.